            "c": "₹300",
            "d": "₹320"
          },
          "correct": "c",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "Let B = x. A = x + 100. x + x + 100 = 700 → 2x = 600 → x = 300. B gets ₹300."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch02_B_004",
          "text": "The perimeter of a rectangle is 68 cm. Its length is 6 cm more than its breadth. The length is:",
