            "d": "24 cm"
          },
          "correct": "b",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "Let breadth = x. Length = x+6. 2(x + x+6) = 68 → 2(2x+6) = 68 → 2x+6 = 34 → 2x = 28 → x = 14. Length = 20 cm."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch02_B_005",
          "text": "Two complementary angles differ by 18°. The larger angle is:",
