          "correct": "d",
          "difficulty": "medium",
          "source": "ncert",
          "explanation": "x - 250 - 180 = x/3 → x - 430 = x/3 → 3x - 1290 = x → 2x = 1290 → x = 645. Verify: 645-430=215=645/3 ✓."
