          "explanation": "Let A = 5x, B = 3x. (5x+6)/(3x+6) = 7/5 → 5(5x+6) = 7(3x+6) → 25x+30 = 21x+42 → 4x = 12 → x = 3. A = 5×3 = 15 years."
        },
        {
          "id": "cbse_8_ch02_D_006",
          "text": "Solve: (x+1)/2 + (x+1)/3 + (x+1)/4 = 13. Find x.",
