          "answer_type": "integer",
          "accepted_forms": [
            "11"
          ],
          "difficulty": "hard",
          "source": "kv_paper",
          "explanation": "Factor (x+1): (x+1)(1/2+1/3+1/4) = 13 → (x+1)(6+4+3)/12 = 13 → (x+1)×13/12 = 13 → x+1 = 12 → x = 11."
        },
